{"surahDetails":{"id":86,"arabicName":"الطارق","banglaName":"রাতের আগন্তুক","englishName":"The Morning Star","enTranslatedName":"At-Tariq","arLocation":"مكية","enLocation":"meccan","totalWords":61,"totalLetters":249,"audio":"http://download.quranicaudio.com/quran/ahmed_ibn_3ali_al-3ajamy/086.mp3","totalAyah":17},"surah":{"id":86,"verses":[{"id":1,"arabic_text":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ وَٱلطَّارِقِ","bangl_text":"শপথ আকাশের এবং রাত্রিতে আগমনকারীর।","english_text":"By the sky and the night comer","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/086001.mp3"},{"id":2,"arabic_text":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلطَّارِقُ","bangl_text":"আপনি জানেন, যে রাত্রিতে আসে সেটা কি","english_text":"And what can make you know what is the night comer","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/086002.mp3"},{"id":3,"arabic_text":"ٱلنَّجۡمُ ٱلثَّاقِبُ","bangl_text":"সেটা এক উজ্জ্বল নক্ষত্র।","english_text":"It is the piercing star","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/086003.mp3"},{"id":4,"arabic_text":"إِن كُلُّ نَفۡسٖ لَّمَّا عَلَيۡهَا حَافِظٞ","bangl_text":"প্রত্যেকের উপর একজন তত্ত্বাবধায়ক রয়েছে।","english_text":"There is no soul but that it has over it a protector","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/086004.mp3"},{"id":5,"arabic_text":"فَلۡيَنظُرِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مِمَّ خُلِقَ","bangl_text":"অতএব, মানুষের দেখা উচিত কি বস্তু থেকে সে সৃজিত হয়েছে।","english_text":"So let man observe from what he was created","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/086005.mp3"},{"id":6,"arabic_text":"خُلِقَ مِن مَّآءٖ دَافِقٖ","bangl_text":"সে সৃজিত হয়েছে সবেগে স্খলিত পানি থেকে।","english_text":"He was created from a fluid, ejected","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/086006.mp3"},{"id":7,"arabic_text":"يَخۡرُجُ مِنۢ بَيۡنِ ٱلصُّلۡبِ وَٱلتَّرَآئِبِ","bangl_text":"এটা নির্গত হয় মেরুদন্ড ও বক্ষপাজরের মধ্য থেকে।","english_text":"Emerging from between the backbone and the ribs","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/086007.mp3"},{"id":8,"arabic_text":"إِنَّهُۥ عَلَىٰ رَجۡعِهِۦ لَقَادِرٞ","bangl_text":"নিশ্চয় তিনি তাকে ফিরিয়ে নিতে সক্ষম।","english_text":"Indeed, Allah, to return him [to life], is Able","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/086008.mp3"},{"id":9,"arabic_text":"يَوۡمَ تُبۡلَى ٱلسَّرَآئِرُ","bangl_text":"যেদিন গোপন বিষয়াদি পরীক্ষিত হবে","english_text":"The Day when secrets will be put on trial","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/086009.mp3"},{"id":10,"arabic_text":"فَمَا لَهُۥ مِن قُوَّةٖ وَلَا نَاصِرٖ","bangl_text":"সেদিন তার কোন শক্তি থাকবে না এবং সাহায্যকারীও থাকবে না।","english_text":"Then man will have no power or any helper","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/086010.mp3"},{"id":11,"arabic_text":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ ذَاتِ ٱلرَّجۡعِ","bangl_text":"শপথ চক্রশীল আকাশের","english_text":"By the sky which returns [rain]","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/086011.mp3"},{"id":12,"arabic_text":"وَٱلۡأَرۡضِ ذَاتِ ٱلصَّدۡعِ","bangl_text":"এবং বিদারনশীল পৃথিবীর","english_text":"And [by] the earth which cracks open","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/086012.mp3"},{"id":13,"arabic_text":"إِنَّهُۥ لَقَوۡلٞ فَصۡلٞ","bangl_text":"নিশ্চয় কোরআন সত্য-মিথ্যার ফয়সালা।","english_text":"Indeed, the Qur'an is a decisive statement","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/086013.mp3"},{"id":14,"arabic_text":"وَمَا هُوَ بِٱلۡهَزۡلِ","bangl_text":"এবং এটা উপহাস নয়।","english_text":"And it is not amusement","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/086014.mp3"},{"id":15,"arabic_text":"إِنَّهُمۡ يَكِيدُونَ كَيۡدٗا","bangl_text":"তারা ভীষণ চক্রান্ত করে","english_text":"Indeed, they are planning a plan","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/086015.mp3"},{"id":16,"arabic_text":"وَأَكِيدُ كَيۡدٗا","bangl_text":"আর আমিও কৌশল করি।","english_text":"But I am planning a plan","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/086016.mp3"},{"id":17,"arabic_text":"فَمَهِّلِ ٱلۡكَٰفِرِينَ أَمۡهِلۡهُمۡ رُوَيۡدَۢا","bangl_text":"অতএব, কাফেরদেরকে অবকাশ দিন, তাদেরকে অবকাশ দিন, কিছু দিনের জন্যে।","english_text":"So allow time for the disbelievers. Leave them awhile","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/086017.mp3"}]}}